看来他找到了
Well, I guess he's found one.

2
00:39:05.469 --> 00:39:07.429 
乔 你很有一套
Joe, you do get around.

3
00:39:07.801 --> 00:39:08.906 
这是你的名字吗
That's your name?

4
00:39:08.951 --> 00:39:10.580 
是个很棒的名字 不是吗
And isn't it a lovely one?

5
00:39:10.666 --> 00:39:12.340 
