So sturdy, so straight.

6
00:39:13.505 --> 00:39:14.560 
别笑
Stop it.

7
00:39:15.060 --> 00:39:16.355 
随便问问 乔
Incidentally, Joe,

8
00:39:17.561 --> 00:39:19.020 
你住哪里
where are you staying?

9
00:39:20.245 --> 00:39:21.386 
这里
Here.

10
00:39:22.352 --> 00:39:23.840 
你住这里
You're staying here?

11
00:39:24.110 --> 00:39:25.804 
这屋子里
In this house?

12
00:39:26.995 --> 00:39:28.990 
是的 这屋子里
Yes, in this house.

13
00:39:30.244 --> 00:39:33.038 
